      [
        ":h2",
        {
          "s": "Skipped — JS-native (for now)"
        }
      ],
      [
        ":p",
        {
          "s": "These views exist to execute user-specified JS code ("
        },
        [
          ":code",
          {
            "s": "new Function(...)"
          }
        ],
        {
          "s": ") and would gain nothing from Hob conversion today. Once Hob is the default user-programming language, inline JS execution becomes the exception rather than the norm — these views may eventually become Hob-native too."
        }
      ],
      [
        ":ul",
        [
          ":li",
          [
            ":p",
            {
              "s": "widget-button-view — executes inline JS on click"
            }
          ]
        ],
        [
          ":li",
          [
            ":p",
            {
              "s": "script-view — displays and runs JS code items"
            }
          ]
        ],
        [
          ":li",
          [
            ":p",
            {
              "s": "widget-checkbox-group-view — executes user JS to load options, unused, poor design-mode UX"
            }
          ]
        ]
      ],
      [
